experiment_start: Welcome in this experiment     Please read the following instructions carefully:     This research is conducted by Coralie Chevallier and Lou Safra from the École Normale Supérieure in Paris. The completed work will be stored in the university laboratory and will remain confidential. The data will be kept for up to three years to facilitate data analysis and interpretation. Participation in this study is voluntary, and you may withdraw at any time. If you choose to answer all the questions it should take a maximum of 30 minutes.    To participate to this study, you must comply with the following conditions:     - You must be 18 years old or more    - You must NOT be a student    - Your monthly income must range between 1301£ and 1775£ (including benefits and revenues from a source other than your professional activities). It is crucial that you comply with this condition. If your income varies from month to month, please only consider the income you have received last month.    Please only complete this study if you comply with all of these conditions. If you do, please proceed with the study by indicating that you agree with the terms and conditions. We thank you in advance for your compliance.     Press the space bar to continue.
